<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Superior Protein Eggs</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#fffdf7;
    color:#333;
}

header{
    background:#ffb347;
    padding:15px 8%;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:800;
    color:#7a3500;
}

nav a{
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-left:25px;
    color:#7a3500;
    font-weight:600;
}

.hero{
    min-height:90vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:50px;
    padding:50px 8%;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.hero-text{
    flex:1;
    min-width:300px;
}

.hero-text h1{
    font-size:60px;
    color:#7a3500;
    line-height:1.1;
}

.hero-text span{
    color:#ff9800;
}

.hero-text p{
    margin-top:20px;
    font-size:18px;
    color:#666;
    max-width:600px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:30px;
    padding:15px 35px;
    background:#ff9800;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:50px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.hero-image{
    flex:1;
    text-align:center;
}

.hero-image img{
    max-width:450px;
    width:100%;
}

.features{
    padding:80px 8%;
    background:white;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:40px;
    color:#7a3500;
    margin-bottom:50px;
}

.feature-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:#fff8e8;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.card h3{
    color:#7a3500;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.products{
    padding:80px 8%;
}

.product-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.product{
    background:white;
    border-radius:20px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.product img{
    width:100%;
    height:220px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.product-info{
    padding:20px;
}

.product-info h4{
    color:#7a3500;
}

.price{
    color:#ff9800;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:bold;
    margin:10px 0;
}

.buy-btn{
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    border:none;
    background:#ff9800;
    color:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

.about{
    padding:80px 8%;
    background:#fff8e8;
    text-align:center;
}

.about p{
    max-width:800px;
    margin:auto;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.contact{
    padding:80px 8%;
}

.contact-box{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
}

input,textarea{
    width:100%;
    padding:15px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    border:1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius:10px;
}

footer{
    background:#7a3500;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){
    .hero-text h1{
        font-size:42px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="logo">🥚 Superior Protein Eggs</div>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#features">Benefits</a>
        <a href="#products">Products</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">

    <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Superior <span>Protein Eggs</span></h1>

        <p>
            Protein You Can Trust. Fresh farm eggs packed with
            premium nutrition, superior quality, and unbeatable taste.
        </p>

        <a href="#products" class="btn">Order Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="egg-mascot.jpg" alt="Superior Protein Eggs">
    </div>

</section>

<section class="features" id="features">

    <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us?</h2>

    <div class="feature-grid">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>💪 High Protein</h3>
            <p>Natural protein source for strength and energy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🥚 Farm Fresh</h3>
            <p>Collected daily with strict quality standards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🌱 Premium Nutrition</h3>
            <p>Rich in vitamins, minerals, and essential nutrients.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>✅ Trusted Quality</h3>
            <p>Safe, hygienic, and consistently superior.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="products" id="products">

<h2 class="section-title">Our Products</h2>

<div class="product-grid">

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569288063643-5d5f1b4efc2e?w=800" alt="">
<div class="product-info">
<h4>Superior Protein Eggs (6 Pack)</h4>
<div class="price">₹60</div>
<button class="buy-btn">Add to Cart</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506976785307-8732e854ad03?w=800" alt="">
<div class="product-info">
<h4>Superior Protein Eggs (12 Pack)</h4>
<div class="price">₹120</div>
<button class="buy-btn">Add to Cart</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587486913049-53fc88980cfc?w=800" alt="">
<div class="product-info">
<h4>Family Pack (30 Eggs)</h4>
<div class="price">₹300</div>
<button class="buy-btn">Add to Cart</button>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="about" id="about">

<h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>

<p>
At Superior Protein Eggs, our mission is simple:
deliver fresh, nutritious, high-protein eggs to every household.
We believe quality nutrition should be affordable, accessible,
and trusted by families across India.
</p>

</section>

<section class="contact" id="contact">

<h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>

<div class="contact-box">

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">

<input type="email" placeholder="Email Address">

<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Message"></textarea>

<button class="buy-btn">
Send Message
</button>

</div>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 Superior Protein Eggs | Protein You Can Trust
</footer>

</body>
</html>
